<%= render partial: 'header' %>
<div class="container">
  <div class="order-forms-container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col s12">
        <ul class="tabs product-features">
          <li class="tab col s3">
            <a href="#pay-on-delivery" class="black-text active">Pay on
              Delivery</a></li>
          <li class="tab col s3 paypal">
            <a href="#pay-with-paypal" class="black-text">Pay with Paypal</a>
          </li>
          <li class="tab col s3">
            <a href="#getmyshop-pay" class="black-text">GetMyShop Pay</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div id="pay-on-delivery" class="col s12">
        <p>Pay cash at your doorstep. You can also use your local Mastercard,
          VISA or Verve card to pay on our POS machine at delivery. We only
          accept Nigerian Naira. We do not accept International cards on POS
          machine at delivery.</p>

        <p>With Pay on Delivery, you are allowed to check your item before
          paying for it. If damaged, broken or doesn't fit, please feel free to
          return immediately</p>

        <h6>Important:</h6>
        <ul>
          <li>
            - Be sure to have the exact amount for payment as our delivery men
            do not carry petty cash.
          </li>
          <li>
            - We only accept Nigerian Naira and local credit cards including
            MasterCard, VISA and Verve.
          </li>
          <li>
            - Maximum amount allowed with Pay on Delivery is N200,000
          </li>
        </ul>

        <div>
          <br>
          <%= button_to "Complete Order", post_payment_orders_path(type: "pay-on-delivery"), class: "btn right" %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div id="pay-with-paypal" class="col s12">
        <%= render "paypal" %>
      </div>
      <div id="getmyshop-pay" class="col s12">
        Not supported yet
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<%= render partial: 'footer' %>
